description:
Description :
        Did the reincarnated noble lady finally win in the group!? Arisa is the protagonist of the "Death March" Extra!! A web-comic spin-off of the super popular "Desuma" series, this is the story of before Satou coming to another world. Arisa's personal secret of her reincarnation is revealed at last with her life of living in another world!
